<li id="cite_note-10"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-10">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBennett" class="citation cs2">Bennett, J. G., <i>Gurdjieff: Making a New World</i></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Gurdjieff%3A+Making+a+New+World&amp;rft.aulast=Bennett&amp;rft.aufirst=J.+G.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABalkh" class="Z3988"></span> Bennett notes <a href="/wiki/Idries_Shah" title="Idries Shah">Idries Shah</a> as the source of the suggestion.</span>
